42
00:02:54,170 --> 00:02:59,960
The article you three will be writing
about sexless women in their thirties.

43
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:02,590
Oh, right.

44
00:03:02,590 --> 00:03:04,850
The Editor-in-chief
proposed we cover the topic.

45
00:03:04,850 --> 00:03:10,120
Sexless relationships
are afflicting younger couples

46
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:12,480
for a variety of reasons.

47
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:15,520
- Interesting.
- It seems a married relationship

48
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:18,610
