seems farfetched for you
and your sexy musician husband, though.

52
00:03:29,540 --> 00:03:34,080
If anything, I feel like the representative.

53
00:03:35,070 --> 00:03:36,990
Huh?

54
00:03:36,990 --> 00:03:40,240
T-The representative of newlywed couples!

55
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:44,850
I can't wait to hear what seasoned wives
have to say about their relationships.

56
00:04:41,020 --> 00:04:45,230
[Episode 2]

57
