59
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:03,550
<i>Then what does that make our relationship?</i>

60
00:05:04,350 --> 00:05:07,070
Sex...

61
00:05:08,930 --> 00:05:10,590
Zero?

62
00:05:23,370 --> 00:05:29,100
<i>Even so, the Ouji I always dreamed of...</i>

63
00:05:29,100 --> 00:05:31,360
<i>will be there as soon as I get home!</i>

64
00:05:32,780 --> 00:05:34,740
