76
00:06:07,350 --> 00:06:10,110
I saw the recipe on my friend's account.

77
00:06:10,110 --> 00:06:12,270
Looked easy enough, so I went to the store.

78
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:13,750
You went to a supermarket?

79
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:15,960
Just give it a try.

80
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,400
I will.

81
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:20,250
Thanks for the meal.

82
00:06:25,090 --> 00:06:27,870
So good!

83
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:29,800
Glad to hear it.

84
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:32,020
This is seriously delicious.

85
00:06:32,020 --> 00:06:34,180
It has an ethnic taste to it.

86
00:06:34,180 --> 00:06:36,890
Right? I thought curry was a difficult dish,

87
00:06:36,890 --> 00:06:39,300
