90
00:06:47,810 --> 00:06:49,850
Sorry.

91
00:06:56,610 --> 00:06:58,170
What?

92
00:06:58,830 --> 00:07:04,010
Living together has made me realize...

93
00:07:04,010 --> 00:07:10,440
you're more put together than I thought.

94
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:13,660
You're honestly a bit maternal sometimes.

95
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:15,450
Say what?

96
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:19,410
Fine, no more cooking for me.

97
00:07:19,410 --> 00:07:21,630
I was kidding! It was a joke!

98
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:24,450
And to think I even bought ice cream for us.

99
00:07:24,450 --> 00:07:26,410
Really?

100
00:07:30,130 --> 00:07:32,290
So sweet...

101
00:07:32,290 --> 00:07:34,340
Is tonight another Something-Moon?

102
00:07:34,340 --> 00:07:36,190
They got too many of those, I'd say.

103
