106
00:07:48,290 --> 00:07:50,520
Honestly, I'd call it a miracle.

107
00:07:54,260 --> 00:07:56,970
Ouji.

108
00:07:58,470 --> 00:08:02,400
<i>I don't want this miracle to end.</i>

109
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:05,400
No, never mind.

110
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:07,680
Whatever you say.

111
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:10,170
<i>I can't ask why.</i>

112
00:08:18,290 --> 00:08:22,420
Being with you is so easy.

113
00:08:23,050 --> 00:08:24,400
Huh?

114
00:08:25,260 --> 00:08:28,020
I guess marriage isn't so bad after all.

115
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:36,360
