118
00:08:43,060 --> 00:08:44,660
Good night.

119
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:59,630
Good night! Sweet dreams!

120
00:09:12,610 --> 00:09:14,190
Haru?

121
00:09:14,190 --> 00:09:16,260
Suzuki! Are you here for work?

122
00:09:16,260 --> 00:09:18,160
Sure am. You here for an interview?

123
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:19,240
Yes.

124
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:22,980
