125
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:26,150
Of course. The pleasure's all mine.

126
00:09:26,950 --> 00:09:31,190
- Thank you for marrying our Ouji.
- Huh?

127
00:09:31,190 --> 00:09:36,920
When I first heard of the marriage,
I honestly thought he'd lost it.

128
00:09:36,920 --> 00:09:39,980
