140
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:33,910
We've been sexless for about 7 years now.

141
00:10:33,910 --> 00:10:36,730
At first, I had made some efforts
to pick things back up again.

142
00:10:36,730 --> 00:10:40,610
Likewise. But there was little point trying
when my husband wouldn't react.

143
00:10:40,610 --> 00:10:44,550
