144
00:10:44,550 --> 00:10:46,950
I tried watching an erotic movie with him.

145
00:10:46,950 --> 00:10:49,050
I wore sexy lingerie for him.

146
00:10:49,050 --> 00:10:50,430
I tried that, too.

147
00:10:50,430 --> 00:10:53,440
