when I tried to massage him, though.

148
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:56,640
That was my husband
when one of my toys went off.

149
00:10:56,640 --> 00:10:57,980
We can only laugh with them.

150
00:10:57,980 --> 00:11:00,460
Yes, I totally understand.

151
00:11:00,460 --> 00:11:04,780
If you're comfortable enough
to laugh off the awkwardness,

152
00:11:04,780 --> 00:11:08,620
