171
00:12:21,740 --> 00:12:23,580
The joys of being a woman?

172
00:12:23,580 --> 00:12:26,340
I'd honestly call her remarks a bit invasive.

173
00:12:30,410 --> 00:12:34,000
Joys of being a woman?

174
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:39,370
