after being married 7 years now.

190
00:13:27,030 --> 00:13:28,460
Dry...

191
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:35,060
Does that mean...

192
00:13:39,170 --> 00:13:40,630
Never mind.

193
00:13:40,630 --> 00:13:42,260
Can I order more cabbage?

194
00:13:42,260 --> 00:13:45,140
- Sounds good.
- Excuse me...

195
00:14:07,210 --> 00:14:09,790
You certainly aren't one
for emotional attachments.

196
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:12,110
Why stay? We're done with our business here.

197
00:14:12,110 --> 00:14:13,740
Business, huh?

198
00:14:13,740 --> 00:14:15,730
You don't ever feel compelled to stay?

199
00:14:15,730 --> 00:14:17,880
Especially with how compatible we are.

200
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:21,420
Nope. I keep my emotional
and physical needs far apart.

201
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:24,510
Sex is just sex, nothing more.

202
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:29,780
Also, I gave it four tries,
but you yap way too much when climaxing.

203
00:14:29,780 --> 00:14:31,260
Bye.

204
00:14:48,340 --> 00:14:49,970
Akina.

205
00:14:55,750 --> 00:14:57,250
<i>Akina.</i>

206
00:14:57,250 --> 00:14:59,850
[Masanori: Don't ignore me.]

207
00:15:03,050 --> 00:15:05,620
