214
00:15:22,750 --> 00:15:25,000
Nothing emotional about that.

215
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:27,080
- Huh?
- "Hearts on the same page"?

216
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:28,580
I feel nothing for you.

217
00:15:28,580 --> 00:15:31,030
No heart, no emotions. Nothing.

218
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:33,000
