225
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:57,240
Keep it down!

226
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:59,420
Sorry.

227
00:15:59,420 --> 00:16:02,370
I guess affairs really do happen in showbiz.

228
00:16:02,370 --> 00:16:09,110
My team is working on a stage play,
